# Stage 2 Report – Project Planning

## Project Title
**Human-in-the-Loop AI Guardian for Connected Aerospace Systems**

## 1. Introduction
This document presents the high-level project plan for the development of the **Human-in-the-Loop AI Guardian for Connected Aerospace Systems**. The purpose of this stage is to organize the project into clear phases, define the major milestones, and provide a structured view of how the work will progress from the initial idea to the final project presentation and closure.

Stage 1 focused on team formation, idea exploration, and MVP selection.  
Stage 2 focuses on planning how the project will be carried out in a realistic, structured, and progressive way.

